Faggotfucks displays this all weird when closing and reopening the browser after following all the steps.
What do?

>only for most to achieve vegetable status from the sheer amount of hatred, anti-semitism and bantz contained within, with the few survivors becoming anons themselves

You think (((they))) will try and shut ZeroNet down or force it to "deplatform" 08gag by putting in a cert blocklist into the default client **which auto-alerts local law enforcement/the ADL upon circumvention**?
What will Meidos do now that there's no mods anymore?

>>917645a9-701f-4df3-ae4c-4092ac9e57db
In all honesty migrating to this here bunker might be for the best.
Old 8gag was already turning into cuckchan on several boards with Feds, boomers and soys shitting up threads all over the place, if and when it does come back online it'll be worse than it's ever been.

>>05bb7b4d-0088-4364-87f5-181605a0171a
I know 8ch wasn't all bad but it just kept getting worse and worse as time went on.
Prospects for improving it are nil with the site infrastructure now in the hands of feds just like it happened to 4chan back in 2008, wouldn't surprise me if moderation of key boards where locked down for mysterious reasons in the near future.
>It is the anons themselves who will need to kick out the outsiders, because most vols are shit and have 0 post quality standards.
Hard to do when such things result in a permaban from the glow in the dark vols and their blackpill BO **as seen on CY+3 and beyond /tech/.**

>>5b1a9810-bdb0-4cc1-83ff-fe2bc2a7d079
I'm on tor and 08chan is faster than Ron's media server ever was.
